    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "ARRIVAL OF CHINA CLIPPER AT PAN AMERICAN AIRPORT, MIAMI, FLORIDA\n32\nPHOTO BY G. W. ROMER\n60705",
      "Man's conquest of the Air\nwas completed with the\nsuccessful crossing of both the Atlantic and Pacific Oceans.\nIt was an exciting event when the conquerer of the Pacific,\nThe China Clipper, landed at the Pan American Air Port.\nPOST CARD\nTHIS SPACE FOR ADDRESS ONLY\nPLACE\nONE CENT\nSTAMP\nHERE\nMADE BY TICHNOR AT BOSTON, MASS.. U S. A.\n202"
